assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Fudo Tetra Corporation engages in the civil engineering, ground improvement, and block environment businesses in Japam. It operates through Civil engineering business, Ground improvement business, and Block business segments. The Civil engineering business segment is involved in the construction of onshore civil engineering work such as roads, tunnels, bridges, and sewers; and marine civil engineering work such as harbors, revetments, and coasts. The Ground improvement business segment engages in the construction of onshore and offshore ground improvement work, the rental of construction machinery, and the sale of related products. The Block business segment provides steel mold for manufacturing wave-dissipating and rooted blocks used for revetments such as harbors, fishing ports, airports, rivers, and coasts. Fudo Tetra Corporation was founded in 1947 and is based in Tokyo, Japan.
